description: Returns information about one or more repositories.

nested_items.name: repositories
nested_items.description: A list of repositories returned by the batch get repositories operation.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account associated with the repository.

nested_items.name: repositoryDescription
nested_items.description: A comment or description about the repository.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: The date and time the repository was last modified, in timestamp format.

nested_items.name: creationDate
nested_items.description: The date and time the repository was created, in timestamp format.

nested_items.name: cloneUrlHttp
nested_items.description: The URL to use for cloning the repository over HTTPS.

nested_items.name: cloneUrlSsh
nested_items.description: The URL to use for cloning the repository over SSH.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the repository.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Key Management Service encryption key used to encrypt and decrypt the repository.

nested_items.name: repositoriesNotFound
nested_items.description: Returns a list of repository names for which information could not be found.

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: Returns information about any errors returned when attempting to retrieve information about the repositories.

nested_items.name: repositoryId
nested_items.description: The ID of a repository that either could not be found or was not in a valid state.

nested_items.name: repositoryName
nested_items.description: The name of a repository that either could not be found or was not in a valid state.

nested_items.name: errorCode
nested_items.description: An error code that specifies the type of failure.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: An error message that provides detail about why the repository either was not found or was not in a valid state.
